{
  "stem": "868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The only reason I could consider climbing over the wall was somehow just opposite the toilets, that part of the wall had some metal rungs stuck all along maybe left over from some repaired job, some masonry job.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I dashed across [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and made my way slowly up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, this may sound incredible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But there was a full moon that-- that night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And above the stable were offices.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as I got higher, I could look into the windows of the offices.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I saw German soldiers there and women soldiers typing, working, office work coming, going.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to myself, oh, my god, how come nobody sees me?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I kept climbing until I reached the four strands of barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, this was the most difficult part.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the barbed wire kept hooking itself into my clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had to take each strand over my hand-- over my head and reach for the next one until I was right on top.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once I was on top, straddling it, this side was the Garrison, here was the street on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At both ends were German sentries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they kept walking back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I figured my best chance is to wait until they are as far away as possible from-- from me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I turned around and let myself hang on the outside, gaining this way, about 6 feet, instead of jumping directly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I let go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Letting go, I scraped the inside of my wrist against the masonry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I fell back on my back, picked myself up, and immediately crossed the street and hid into the entrance of-- of a building.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
